<p>When viewing a book's details, users also want to get information about the author or authors. The details should include:</p>
<ul class="simple">
<li>Full name</li>
<li>Date of birth</li>
<li>Date of death (If deceased)</li>
<li>A list of other books written by them. (If more than 5, the 6th entry&nbsp;can be a link to a complete bibliography page.)</li>
</ul>
